<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Charge Rental</title>
    </head>
    <body
        style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;"
    >
        <div
            style="
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            border: 1px solid #016670; 
            background-color: #EDEAE5; 
            padding: 20px;"
        >
            <div
                style="
                text-align: center; 
                margin-bottom: 10px;"
            >
                <a href="https://imgur.com/KtlxJ1X"><img
                        src="https://i.imgur.com/KtlxJ1X.png"
                        title="source: imgur.com"
                    /></a>
            </div>

            <div style="color: #016670; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <h1>Dear, {{name}}!</h1>
                <p>We hope this email finds you well. We regret to inform you that your booking with Charge Car has been canceled.
                </p>
            </div>
            <hr />
            <div style="padding: 20px; background-color: #fdf9f1; ">
                <h2 style="font-size: 18px; color: #016670;">Booking Details</h2>
                <hr style="margin: 10px 0;" />
                <p><strong>Car Model:</strong> {{carmodel}} </p>
                <p><strong>Pick-up Date:</strong> {{formattedStartDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Return Date:</strong> {{formattedEndDate}}</p>
                <p>
                    The total cost is
                    ${{totalcost}}
                    and we have refund your Payment Card ending in
                    {{cardinfo}}.
                </p>
                <hr />
                <p>
                    Thank you for considering Charge Car for your rental needs. 
                    We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused and look forward to serving you in the future.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div style="padding: 15px">
                <p style="color: #016670;">For every rental, you're making a
                    positive impact by choosing our green cars. Thank you for
                    helping us contribute to a more sustainable future.</p>
            </div>
            <div
                style="background-color: #016670; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff;"
            >
                <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding the cancellations, feel free to
                    contact our support team.</p>
            </div>

            <footer
                style="
                text-align: center; 
                margin-top: 20px;
                font-size: 10px;"
            >
                <p>
                    &copy;
                    {{year}}
                    Charge
                </p>
                <p>Email: electricchargecars@gmail.com | Phone: +65 88334669</p>

            </footer>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>